body:
I get an error when I convert the module `GetInsnPtr` shown below to verilog with sv2v and read it in yosys. The version of sv2v is `v0.0.9-27-g5e17ef0`.

```
 Yosys 0.16+41 (git sha1 UNKNOWN, clang 3.9.1-19ubuntu1 -fPIC -Os)


yosys> read_verilog -sv GetInstPtr.v 
1. Executing Verilog-2005 frontend: GetInstPtr.v
Parsing SystemVerilog input from `GetInstPtr.v' to AST representation.
Generating RTLIL representation for module `\GetInsnPtr'.
GetInstPtr.v:21: ERROR: 2nd expression of procedural for-loop is not constant!
```

Part of the original code (https://github.com/rsd-devel/rsd/blob/8777d59e0b9aa06e4df06711d00754a2f8a51d8b/Processor/Src/Pipeline/CommitStage.sv#L55-L77):
```verilog
module GetInsnPtr(
    output logic headOfThisInsn[2],
    input  logic last [2]
);
    always_comb begin
        for (int i = 0; i < 2; i++) begin
            headOfThisInsn[i] = 0;
            for (int j = i - 1; 0 <= j; j--) begin
                if (last[j]) begin
                    headOfThisInsn[i] = j + 1;
                    break;
                end
            end
        end
    end
endmodule
```

Code converted by sv2v: 
```verilog
module GetInsnPtr (
	headOfThisInsn,
	last
);
	output reg [0:1] headOfThisInsn;
	input wire [0:1] last;
	always @(*) begin : sv2v_autoblock_1
		reg [0:1] _sv2v_jump;
		_sv2v_jump = 2'b00;
		begin : sv2v_autoblock_2
			reg signed [31:0] i;
			for (i = 0; i < 2; i = i + 1)
				if (_sv2v_jump < 2'b10) begin
					_sv2v_jump = 2'b00;
					headOfThisInsn[i] = 0;
					begin : sv2v_autoblock_3
						reg signed [31:0] j;
						begin : sv2v_autoblock_4
							reg [0:1] _sv2v_jump_1;
							_sv2v_jump_1 = _sv2v_jump;
							for (j = i - 1; (0 <= j) && (_sv2v_jump < 2'b10); j = (_sv2v_jump < 2'b10 ? j - 1 : j))
								begin
									_sv2v_jump = 2'b00;
									if (last[j]) begin
										headOfThisInsn[i] = j + 1;
										_sv2v_jump = 2'b10;
									end
								end
							if (_sv2v_jump != 2'b11)
								_sv2v_jump = _sv2v_jump_1;
						end
					end
				end
			if (_sv2v_jump != 2'b11)
				_sv2v_jump = 2'b00;
		end
	end
endmodule
```

